                <note rend="inline" type="source">740.00118 European War (1939)/1885:
                    Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">William Phillips</persName>,
                        Personal Representative of President <persName>Roosevelt</persName> in
                        India, to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">New Delhi</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-03-26">March 26,
                            1943</date>.<lb/>[Received March 26—10:08 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>240. Department’s 161, 18th. Government of India has now informed Mission that
                    assignments will be agreeable.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Phillips</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
